      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8">Your best customers are already mobile-first, and expect an app experience that makes browsing, bundling, and reordering effortless. This guide shows Home & Kitchen brands the fastest, lowest-risk path to a high-performing app using MobiLoud’s fully managed website-to-app service, with proof points, process, and an action plan.</p>
